==English==
===Etymology===
Shortened from '''[[Pakistani]]'''

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æki|-æki]]

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun|s}}

#(''derogatory, offensive and racist'') A [[Pakistani]], or, more generally, a person who is perceived to be a Pakistani; often applied to persons of any South Asian or Middle Eastern origin - or indeed any immigrant due to them not being educated about foreign nationals from the asian continent.

===Proper adjective===
{{en-adj-notcomp}}

#(''derogatory, offensive and racist when spoken by non-Pakistanis'') [[Pakistani]], or perceived to be Pakistani.